	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div xml:id="div1" corresp="regest1">
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Gratiam et pacem a domino.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Summa cum laetitia et expectatione tuas accepi literas<note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1">Oben <ref target="file11712">Nr. 1669</ref>f.</note>, charissime <persName ref="p3700" cert="high">Eberharte</persName>, et ago tibi gratias immortales.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ubi descripsero exemplum,<note xml:id="fn2" type="footnote" n="2">Die Rede ist vielleicht von der Briefbeilage, die Exzerpte zur eidgenössischen Geschichte enthielt (vgl. oben <ref target="file11712">Nr. 1669</ref>, 37-41).</note> remittam.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Exemplaria duo<note xml:id="fn3" type="footnote" n="3">Gemeint sind Exemplare von <persName ref="p495" type="auto_name">Bullingers</persName> Matthäuskommentar; vgl. oben <ref target="file11713">Nr. 1670</ref>, 11-13.</note> constant 28 batz.<pb type="edition" next="204"/></s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Scripsi  <persName ref="p8401" cert="high">Conzeno</persName><note xml:id="fn4" type="footnote" n="4"><persName ref="p8401" cert="high">Peter Kunz</persName>.</note> sicut petisti<note xml:id="fn5" type="footnote" n="5">Vgl. oben <ref target="file11712">Nr. 1669</ref>, 26-36. 56f; 1670, 17-25.</note> d. <persName ref="p8437" cert="high">Erasmi</persName><note xml:id="fn6" type="footnote" n="6"><persName ref="p8437" cert="high">Erasmus Schmid</persName>; vgl. oben <ref target="file11712">Nr. 1669</ref>, Anm. 3.</note> et meo nomine.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quod puerum attinet quaestoris aerarii<note xml:id="fn7" type="footnote" ana="bio" n="7"><persName ref="p3700" cert="high">Rümlang</persName> hatte den aus <placeName ref="l503" cert="high">Thun</placeName> stammenden (Pflege-?)Sohn eines Säckelmeisters empfohlen; vgl. oben <ref target="file11713">Nr. 1670</ref>, 1-9.</note>, vellem actum esse prudentius.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p1214" cert="high">Frisius</persName><note xml:id="fn8" type="footnote" n="8"><persName ref="p1214" cert="high">Johannes Fries</persName>.</note> est vir diligens et bonus, sed in uno contubernio fovet adolescentes 20. Potes ipse cogitare, quam impediantur multitudine studia.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ego apud d. <persName ref="p8400" cert="high">Petrum Cholinum</persName><note xml:id="fn9" type="footnote" n="9"><persName ref="p8400" cert="high">Peter Kolin</persName>.</note>, virum doctissimum et integerrimum, ipsi hospitium impetraram, lectum ipse daturus fueram; quoniam vero <persName ref="p1214" cert="high">Frisio</persName> commendatus fuerat, ego facile cessi.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Oro, ut scribas, si quid habes ex <placeName ref="l834" cert="high">Italia</placeName> vel Gallia de nostris exercitibus.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Puto <persName ref="p1227" cert="high">Froschouerum</persName> brevi <placeName ref="l41" cert="high">Bernam</placeName> venturum.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Plura nunc non potui, plura alioqui scripsissem.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale iterum cum omnibus bonis.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name">Tiguri</placeName>, 4. octobris anno 1542.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p495" type="auto_name">H. Bullinger</persName>us.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse auf der Rückseite:]</note>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Domino <persName ref="p3700" cert="high">Eberharto a Rümlang</persName>, suo in domino charissimo fratri.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
